Juxtaposition of French and Estonian in different aspects: syntax, semantics, lexis, phraseology. Exercises in contrastive analysis.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The course provides an overview of aims and methods of contrastive linguistics and gives the students initial experience in systematic contrastive analysis of French and Estonian.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The student who has successfully completed the course - knows and is able to apply the main research methods of contrastive linguistics; - knows the essential similarities and differences between French and Estonian in areas discussed in the course; - knows the errors caused by French-Estonian interference and is able to avoid them.
